                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020113-55-defend578 t18020113-55-punish294"></join>
               Confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Rooke.</p>
